    "This last examples focuses on combining SD and SEM within the same study to better understand the relationship between systems thinking and team performance in an undergraduate course.",
    "Of particular interest here is the use of SEM to establish the latent structure of \"systems thinking\" using the Systems Thinking Scale Revised (STSR) (Davis and Stroink, 2016).",
    "STSR has been previously used and analyzed as a unidimensional measure of systems thinking (Davis and Stroink, 2016; Davis et al. 2018; Ballew et al 2019).",
    "In this paper, we have highlighted the differences between structural equation modeling and system dynamics, and then sought to develop a general framework in an effort to bridge the \"unavoidable a priori\" between two different approaches to causal modeling.",
